        "action": "Rewrite OFGEM'S policy rules to prioritise Net Zero carbon emissions",
        "additional_details": "See article by Jillian Ambrose, Energy Correspondent of The Guardian, dated Monday 22 July, 2019: 'Energy regulator is out of touch over climate crisis, say businesses.'\r\nhttps://www.theguardian.com/business/2019/jul/22/energy-regulator-is-out-of-touch-over-climate-crisis-say-businesses-ofgem",
        "background": "OFGEM is the UK's energy regulator. Its statutory policy guidelines were last revised in 2011 and are incompatible with the UK Government's goal of reducing our carbon emissions to net zero by AD 2050. OFGEM bureaucracy is frustrating efforts to prioritize clean growth and progress towards net zero.",
